<paragraph id="A71087DD122187374C8C3939D1A0061D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
PERU. Apurimac, 
<emphasis id="941FDC36DDD3E9DA4811F57BA28B5F95" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A. Weberbauer</emphasis>
5875, holotype B†, isotypes: F, GH, US).
</paragraph>
